<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Rothenburg ob der Tauber</head><p>Der Rat bedauert den Streit zwischen Heinrich von Sickingen und Dienern der Adressaten in Walbach und kündigt wie gewünscht eine Gesandtschaft für Dienstag vor Georgstag nach Mergentheim an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_143" id="71v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_143_r2l15">Den von <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_143_r2l16"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des handels <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> der ſıch <expan>ʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l17"><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>Sıkıng<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>etlıch<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> . vnd <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> dıenern ʒu vvalbach <expan>v<ex>er</ex>loffen</expan> hat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l18">etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Vnd mag vns eẅr <expan>freẅntſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> wol getrawn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l19">daʒ vns das . vnd was eẅch oder den <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> ſchadens <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex>drıeſſ</expan> beſcheh </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l20"><expan>getreẅl<ex>ich</ex></expan> laıd ıſt / Vnd ob wır ıht rede <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> hören <expan>wurde<ex>n</ex></expan> . daʒ wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l21">eẅch darin <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>antwurten</expan> <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Vnd als Jr vns <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l22">eẅch . <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erbe<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> . ʒu dem tag gen <expan>Mergenth<ex>eim</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> . auf den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l23">Ertag vor ſand <expan>görg<ex>en</ex></expan> tag ſchıerıſt / Das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tun . Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l24">bıtten eẅr <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> Ob der tag <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex>botten</expan> wurd <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> niht fürgank </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l25">gewunne . daʒ Jr vns das ʒu <expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒeıt <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıbt</expan> <expan>alſu<ex>er</ex>r</expan> Jr mugt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l27">Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l26"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>vıgı<ex>lia</ex></expan> Paſche </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_143" id="71v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde,</ex></expan> als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des handels
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, der sich
                            <expan>zwisch<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>Siking<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>etlich<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> dienern zu
                        Walbach <expan>v<ex>er</ex>loffen</expan> hat etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                        Und mag uns ewr <expan>frewnts<ex>chaft</ex></expan> wol getrawn, daz uns
                        das und, was ewch oder den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> schadens
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex>driess</expan> bescheh,
                            <expan>getrewl<ex>ich</ex></expan> laid ist und, ob wir iht rede
                                <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> hören <expan>wurde<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        daz wir ewch darin <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>antwurten</expan>
<expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Und als ir uns
                            <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> habt, ewch
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erbe<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> zu dem tag gen
                            <expan>Mergenth<ex>eim</ex></expan> zu <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        auf den <app><note><q type="date">ertag vor sand <expan>Görg<ex>en</ex></expan> tag schierist</q>16.04.1415</note></app>, das
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tun.
                        Und bitten ewr <expan>weish<ex>eit,</ex></expan> ob der tag
                                <expan>wid<ex>er</ex>botten</expan> wurd
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> niht fürgank gewunne, daz ir uns das zu
                                <expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan> zeit
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreibt</expan>, <expan>alsv<ex>er</ex>r</expan> ir
                        mugt; denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>vigi<ex>lia</ex></expan> pasche. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
